1.1.name: wordpress/wp-tagcanvas
1.1.description: Get a 3D Tag cloud by TagCanvas(http://www.goat1000.com/tagcanvas.php).TagCanvas is a Javascript class which will draw and animate a HTML5 canvas based tag cloud. It support three shape:sphere, hcylinder for a cylinder that starts off horizontal and vcylinder for a cylinder that starts off vertical. Based on TagCanvas version 1.12.
